withdraw_message: Enter the amount and the wallet address to which you want to send.
deposit_message: Tap to copy the address into clipboard and send from your external wallet. After confirmation the amount will appear in your trading wallet and is held by Tagcash untill you withdraw.
deposit_php_message: Choose your bank and method to deposit, deposit into the Account as indicated and confirm your deposit here. There are no charges for depositing,  and the amount is confirmed within one day or faster depending on day and time confirmation is sent.
cashout_message: Choose your bank and method to cashout and click request. Cashout will be done within 1 business day.
amount_deducted_message: Total amount to be deducted from your Tagcash Account
pesos_charged_fee: 20 pesos wil be charged as fee
mobile_person_pickup: Mobile number of person to pickup
seven_eleven_message: Go to any 7-Eleven and show the barcode that is generated by the button below. The amount is immediately deposited into your account, less 2% fee that 7-Eleven keeps. For example, you generate a code for 100 Pesos, and give that to the cashier at 7-Eleven, and 98 Pesos will be credited to your account.
scan_qr_message: Scan the QR code below or use the address provided to deposit funds directly into your wallet. You can check the approximate rate you will receive before you transfer. The amount will be credited to your account within 1 confirmation.
